  <brief_title>Does Preoperative Caldolor Decrease the Requirement for Postoperative Narcotics</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does Preoperative Caldolor Decrease the Requirement for Postoperative Narcotics in Patients Undergoing Laparoscopic or Open Inguinal and/or Umbilical Hernia Repair? A Randomized, Double-Blind, Prospective Trial</official_title>
